1
00:00:07,958 --> 00:00:11,000
[CROWD screams]

2
00:00:13,541 --> 00:00:15,375
And now, you will
pay for the crime

3
00:00:15,458 --> 00:00:17,291
of endangering the lives
of innocent people!

4
00:00:17,375 --> 00:00:18,000
[CRAB GUILDY grunts]

5
00:00:18,083 --> 00:00:19,250
[ULTIROIDS]
Moge!

6
00:00:19,333 --> 00:00:21,666
Time to go back to
the ocean, crab freak!

7
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:24,000
[TAILYELLOW grunts]
Uh?!

8
00:00:24,083 --> 00:00:26,125
--[CRAB GUILDY] Uh...
--[ULTROIDS murmur]

9
00:00:26,208 --> 00:00:28,291
Ah, I have other
weapons I can use!

10
00:00:28,375 --> 00:00:31,000
Like my deadly Voltic Blaster!

11
00:00:32,625 --> 00:00:34,000
Crap.

12
00:02:05,166 --> 00:02:08,083
I don't get it, why is
this happening to me?

13
00:02:08,166 --> 00:02:09,541
I hope she pulls through.

14
00:02:09,625 --> 00:02:12,875
This doesn't make sense.
She transformed and everything.

15
00:02:12,958 --> 00:02:16,208
Wait. We have to deal
with Crab Guildy first!

16
00:02:16,291 --> 00:02:19,041
Aura Pillar! Ha!

17
00:02:20,625 --> 00:02:21,791
[CRAB GUILDY]
Uh?!

18
00:02:21,875 --> 00:02:23,458
[ULTIROIDS scream]

19
00:02:23,541 --> 00:02:25,833
Execute Wave! Ha!

20
00:02:27,875 --> 00:02:30,625
[CRAB GUILDY groans]

21
00:02:34,208 --> 00:02:35,291
[CRAB GUILDY]
I only wish

22
00:02:35,375 --> 00:02:37,291
I could've seen the
backs of more necks.

23
00:02:37,375 --> 00:02:39,375
[CRAB GUILDY screams]

24
00:02:44,208 --> 00:02:45,583
[TAILYELLOW cries]

25
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:58,500
[ERINA] I've decided I'm not
worthy of this bracelet, Soji.

26
00:02:58,583 --> 00:02:59,333
Here.

27
00:02:59,416 --> 00:03:00,458
[SOJI]
Huh?

28
00:03:00,541 --> 00:03:02,458
[ERINA]
As much as I want to be a hero.

29
00:03:02,541 --> 00:03:04,375
The truth is, I just don't
think I have what it takes

30
00:03:04,458 --> 00:03:07,375
to fight next to you and Aika
and take down Ultimaguil.

31
00:03:07,458 --> 00:03:09,000
You're being too
hard on yourself.

32
00:03:09,083 --> 00:03:12,083
Aika and I've been studying
martial arts since we were kids.

33
00:03:12,166 --> 00:03:13,458
Just give it a
little bit of time,

34
00:03:13,541 --> 00:03:15,791
and I promise you'll get
there eventually.

35
00:03:15,875 --> 00:03:17,500
Just cause you can't use
your power right away

36
00:03:17,583 --> 00:03:18,500
doesn't mean you
won't come around--

37
00:03:18,583 --> 00:03:20,791
No, you're wrong!

38
00:03:20,875 --> 00:03:23,208
Excuse me. But would
you three mind

39
00:03:23,291 --> 00:03:26,041
giving me a minute
alone with Soji, please?

40
00:03:26,125 --> 00:03:28,125
Are you sure, miss?

41
00:03:33,625 --> 00:03:36,291
We have to be real. Tail Gear
only works effectively when

42
00:03:36,375 --> 00:03:39,166
the person wearing it has
a deep love for twin-tails.

43
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:40,458
That's the deal, right?

44
00:03:40,541 --> 00:03:42,375
Yeah. After all,

45
00:03:42,458 --> 00:03:45,416
It was constructed around
a core of twin-tail attribute.

46
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:48,375
To be honest with you,
when I first transformed.

47
00:03:48,458 --> 00:03:50,333
I had this bad feeling,
deep in my heart,

48
00:03:50,416 --> 00:03:52,041
that I wasn't going to
be able to make it work.

49
00:03:52,125 --> 00:03:53,291
[SOJI]
Hm.

50
00:03:53,375 --> 00:03:55,125
[ERINA] There's something
you should know.

51
00:03:55,208 --> 00:03:58,125
I don't like twin-tails,
and I never have.

52
00:03:58,208 --> 00:03:59,541
Hold on. What?!

53
00:03:59,625 --> 00:04:00,750
[AIKA, TWOEARLE, MIKOTO gasp]

54
00:04:00,833 --> 00:04:03,000
Madam President.
Why would you lie like that?

55
00:04:03,083 --> 00:04:06,166
That may be the most hurtful
lie I've ever heard.

56
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:07,750
I admire you, Soji.

57
00:04:07,833 --> 00:04:10,875
I've never met anybody who loves
twin-tails as much as you do.

58
00:04:10,958 --> 00:04:12,375
[SOJI exhales]

59
00:04:12,458 --> 00:04:15,125
But I'm not you. I don't
wear my hair like this

60
00:04:15,208 --> 00:04:18,125
because I want to or
because I think it's cute.

61
00:04:18,208 --> 00:04:20,416
I wear my hair in twin-tails
because my mother tells

62
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,791
me to and in my house we
always do what we're told.

63
00:04:22,875 --> 00:04:25,666
Shindo family rules are
not allowed to be broken.

64
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:27,375
That seems a little
overdramatic.

65
00:04:27,458 --> 00:04:29,125
[ERINA] Soji, I've been
forced to wear my hair

66
00:04:29,208 --> 00:04:31,583
like this for as long
as I can remember!

67
00:04:31,666 --> 00:04:34,125
People always tell me it makes
me look like a little kid.

68
00:04:34,208 --> 00:04:37,875
I do, but it's not like I have
a choice in the matter.

69
00:04:37,958 --> 00:04:40,291
[ERINA] Even though I should've
been angry with my parents

70
00:04:40,375 --> 00:04:44,166
for forcing my hand, instead, I
took my anger out on twin-tails.

71
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:46,375
I figured that since I had
to dress like a child,

72
00:04:46,458 --> 00:04:48,625
I could be petulant
like one as well.

73
00:04:48,708 --> 00:04:50,333
I blamed everything
on twin-tails.

74
00:04:50,416 --> 00:04:52,833
My unhappiness,
my suffering, all of it.

75
00:04:52,916 --> 00:04:55,083
And I've hated them ever since.

76
00:04:55,166 --> 00:04:58,291
Oh, wow. That's so terrible.

77
00:04:58,375 --> 00:05:00,083
Regardless, I still do my duty.

78
00:05:00,166 --> 00:05:02,583
I wear my hair like this,
in spite of it all.

79
00:05:02,666 --> 00:05:05,041
But because I respect you,
I want you to know the truth.

80
00:05:05,125 --> 00:05:07,083
And that is, I don't
even like twin-tails.

81
00:05:07,166 --> 00:05:08,500
Look. Madame president.

82
00:05:08,583 --> 00:05:10,500
It doesn't matter
if you like them.

83
00:05:10,583 --> 00:05:11,375
[ERINA]
Uh!

84
00:05:11,458 --> 00:05:12,875
[SOJI]
You're one of us now,

85
00:05:12,958 --> 00:05:15,125
and nothing that happened in
your past will change that.

86
00:05:15,208 --> 00:05:18,625
Plus. You may think that
you don't love twin-tails,

87
00:05:18,708 --> 00:05:20,250
but I'm pretty sure
that's not the case.

88
00:05:20,333 --> 00:05:21,916
Sorry, Soji, but it's true!

89
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,333
Well, let's agree to disagree.

90
00:05:23,416 --> 00:05:26,916
I can tell just by looking
at your twin-tails.

91
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,375
[ERINA sighs]

92
00:05:30,166 --> 00:05:32,083
[LEVIAGUILDY] First, they
take out Buffalo Guildy,

93
00:05:32,166 --> 00:05:33,916
one of my strongest warriors,

94
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,583
and then Crab Guildy,
one of yours.

95
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:39,333
They were both easily
destroyed by the Twin Tails.

96
00:05:39,416 --> 00:05:41,458
[KRAKEGUILDY] Dark Grasper
is not only the chief's

97
00:05:41,541 --> 00:05:45,875
own personal inspector, but
his dark executioner as well.

98
00:05:45,958 --> 00:05:47,750
[KRAKEGUILDY] According
to the rumors I've heard,

99
00:05:47,833 --> 00:05:50,041
units that are incapable of
carrying out their mission

100
00:05:50,125 --> 00:05:52,958
are dealt with mercilessly. And
not just the captains, either.

101
00:05:53,041 --> 00:05:55,000
Their soldiers are
punished as well.

102
00:05:55,083 --> 00:05:57,291
[LEVIAGUILDY]
Wait. You mean executed?

103
00:05:57,375 --> 00:05:59,208
If it were just me,
that would be one thing.

104
00:05:59,291 --> 00:06:01,750
But the lives of my men, too?

105
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,541
[SPARROW GUILDY]
We must work together.

106
00:06:05,625 --> 00:06:07,083
[LEVIAGUILDY]
Yes.

107
00:06:07,166 --> 00:06:10,500
I suppose this is no time to be
bickering about breast-size.

108
00:06:10,583 --> 00:06:11,708
[KRAKEGUILDY]
Mm.

109
00:06:11,791 --> 00:06:13,958
First, we must take
care of the Twin Tails.

110
00:06:14,041 --> 00:06:16,750
After they're properly
dispatched. Flat chests--

111
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:18,291
[LEVIAGUILDY]
Or giant breasts!

112
00:06:18,375 --> 00:06:21,458
[KRAKEGUILDY] Is a matter we
can settle when the job is done.

113
00:06:21,541 --> 00:06:23,708
[ERINA growls]
I don't understand.

114
00:06:23,791 --> 00:06:25,541
Why are you so obsessed
with twin-tails,

115
00:06:25,625 --> 00:06:27,708
can you at least explain
that much to me?

116
00:06:27,791 --> 00:06:29,166
[SOJI]
I don't know.

117
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:31,458
I suppose I could ask you
the same thing about heroes.

118
00:06:31,541 --> 00:06:32,916
[ERINA]
Heroes?

119
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,625
Well, I like them
because they're cool.

120
00:06:34,708 --> 00:06:36,916
They protect innocents,
and put their lives on the line

121
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,958
every day to keep
the world safe!

122
00:06:39,041 --> 00:06:40,791
They fight for what
they believe in.

123
00:06:40,875 --> 00:06:41,958
No matter what course they take,

124
00:06:42,041 --> 00:06:44,000
heroes stay true to
who they really are!

125
00:06:44,083 --> 00:06:46,583
Can you say that
about twin-tails?

126
00:06:46,666 --> 00:06:48,708
I think there are a lot
of wonderful things

127
00:06:48,791 --> 00:06:51,875
about twin-tails. Who knows,
maybe I'm completely nuts.

128
00:06:51,958 --> 00:06:53,958
Maybe I'm unstable. After all,

129
00:06:54,041 --> 00:06:57,083
what kind of lunatic would
risk his life over twin-tails?

130
00:06:57,166 --> 00:06:58,750
It does sound a little crazy.

131
00:06:58,833 --> 00:07:00,916
But all that's just
a front, isn't it, Soji?

132
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,500
You protect others, too.

133
00:07:02,583 --> 00:07:05,083
Getting to fight for twin-tails
is merely the icing on the cake!

134
00:07:05,166 --> 00:07:07,375
Whoa, hold on.
You're dead wrong!

135
00:07:07,458 --> 00:07:08,833
Defending twin-tails
isn't the icing.

136
00:07:08,916 --> 00:07:11,500
Defending twin-tails
is the cake!

137
00:07:11,583 --> 00:07:13,333
You really mean that?

138
00:07:13,416 --> 00:07:14,291
[SOJI]
Are you put off?

139
00:07:14,375 --> 00:07:15,708
Uh. No, I...

140
00:07:15,791 --> 00:07:17,291
I don't know yet.

141
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:19,875
[SOJI] It's just like you and
your heroes, Madam President.

142
00:07:19,958 --> 00:07:22,291
Other people might think
it's lame or stupid.

143
00:07:22,375 --> 00:07:23,875
But for me?

144
00:07:23,958 --> 00:07:26,333
Twin-tails are the most amazing
thing I've seen in this world.

145
00:07:26,416 --> 00:07:30,500
And I don't care what anyone
else has to say about it.

146
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:32,041
Yes, I suppose you're right.

147
00:07:32,125 --> 00:07:35,125
Which is exactly why I'm gonna
stop those Elemelian jerks!

148
00:07:35,208 --> 00:07:36,708
Those monsters
at Ultimaguil think

149
00:07:36,791 --> 00:07:39,000
they can do whatever they want.
They think they can subjugate

150
00:07:39,083 --> 00:07:42,041
entire worlds of people and
take away the things they love!

151
00:07:42,125 --> 00:07:44,625
But I'm not gonna
let that happen.

152
00:07:44,708 --> 00:07:48,083
I'm gonna defend those people
by defending twin-tails.

153
00:07:48,166 --> 00:07:50,583
Because that's the
only thing I can do.

154
00:07:50,666 --> 00:07:53,208
It doesn't matter if
everyone thinks I'm crazy.

155
00:07:53,291 --> 00:07:55,458
As long as I have friends who
I can share my feelings with,

156
00:07:55,541 --> 00:07:58,000
and who are brave
enough to fight with me,

157
00:07:58,083 --> 00:08:00,833
then I consider myself
to be a lucky guy.

158
00:08:00,916 --> 00:08:03,125
You could be one of
those friends, Erina.

159
00:08:03,208 --> 00:08:04,500
[ERINA]
Uh!

160
00:08:04,583 --> 00:08:05,625
[SOJI]
Uh!

161
00:08:05,708 --> 00:08:08,166
Sorry. I mean Madame president.

162
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:10,375
[ERINA panting]

163
00:08:10,458 --> 00:08:11,500
[SOJI]
Oh no,

164
00:08:11,583 --> 00:08:13,250
you're hyperventilating.

165
00:08:13,333 --> 00:08:15,666
Erina is fine. [exhales]

166
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,250
[SOJI]
Uh!

167
00:08:17,333 --> 00:08:19,333
Madame president,
your twin-tails.

168
00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:20,458
They glowed.

169
00:08:20,541 --> 00:08:21,750
What are you talking about?

170
00:08:21,833 --> 00:08:23,041
That isn't possible.

171
00:08:23,125 --> 00:08:25,458
[SOJI]
I saw it with my own eyes!

172
00:08:25,541 --> 00:08:27,083
I wanna tell you something.

173
00:08:27,166 --> 00:08:28,583
[SOJI]
Uh?

174
00:08:28,666 --> 00:08:31,458
I may not love twin-tails like
you, but I wanna be a hero

175
00:08:31,541 --> 00:08:33,791
more than I've ever wanted
anything in my entire life.

176
00:08:33,875 --> 00:08:35,458
So if you wanna fight
to defend twin-tails,

177
00:08:35,541 --> 00:08:37,958
then I wanna fight
to become a hero!

178
00:08:38,041 --> 00:08:39,708
But, I guess it doesn't matter,

179
00:08:39,791 --> 00:08:42,000
since I can't control
the Tail Gear's power.

180
00:08:42,083 --> 00:08:43,083
Uh!

181
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,375
Erina.

182
00:08:46,458 --> 00:08:47,958
[ERINA]
Uh...

183
00:08:48,041 --> 00:08:50,250
[SOJI] I've got a crazy idea,
would you go along with it?

184
00:08:50,333 --> 00:08:50,708
Wait.

185
00:08:50,791 --> 00:08:51,666
Seriously?

186
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:52,541
Okay.

187
00:08:52,625 --> 00:08:53,875
Special training, am I right?

188
00:08:53,958 --> 00:08:55,458
[ERINA]
Uh!

189
00:08:55,541 --> 00:08:58,250
That's what I was gonna say, but
now you've spoiled all the fun.

190
00:08:58,333 --> 00:08:59,958
What kind of special training?

191
00:09:00,041 --> 00:09:01,500
--Erina.
--[ERINA] Mm?

192
00:09:01,583 --> 00:09:03,958
If you're weak,
you just need to get stronger.

193
00:09:04,041 --> 00:09:05,291
Once you've built
up your stamina,

194
00:09:05,375 --> 00:09:07,125
you'll master your
Tail Gear in no time!

195
00:09:07,208 --> 00:09:08,916
[ERINA]
Uh! All right, then.

196
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,708
I'm ready when you are!

197
00:09:10,791 --> 00:09:12,291
[SOJI]
Yeah! That's the spirit!

198
00:09:12,375 --> 00:09:13,500
Just be yourself.

199
00:09:13,583 --> 00:09:15,541
And show us all exactly
who you really are.

200
00:09:15,625 --> 00:09:17,291
[ERINA gasps]

201
00:09:17,375 --> 00:09:21,125
Ah. So that's what
all this is about, huh?

202
00:09:21,208 --> 00:09:22,666
I'm finally starting
to understand

203
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,583
how Miss Erina thinks,
and I like it.

204
00:09:24,666 --> 00:09:26,291
--[alarm rings]
--[ALL] Uh?!

205
00:09:26,375 --> 00:09:28,833
It sounds like
we've got company!

206
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:35,375
[SOJI]
Elemelians?

207
00:09:35,458 --> 00:09:37,666
But what are they doing
in such a deserted place?

208
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:39,208
It doesn't make sense.

209
00:09:39,291 --> 00:09:42,625
Crap. And they picked
the worst possible time!

210
00:09:42,708 --> 00:09:44,250
I guess training will
have to come later.

211
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:46,041
[AIKA] You go ahead.
I can handle this!

212
00:09:46,125 --> 00:09:47,208
--[SOJI] Uh?
--[ERINA] Mm?

213
00:09:47,291 --> 00:09:48,750
Haven't you been
paying attention

214
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:51,416
to my demolishing rate lately?
Look, don't worry about it,

215
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:53,666
I can take care of a couple
of dumb Elemelians.

216
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:55,125
[SOJI]
No way.

217
00:09:55,208 --> 00:09:56,791
If Miss Aika says she can
take care of this situation,

218
00:09:56,875 --> 00:09:59,708
then I believe her.
Now let's start "training"!

219
00:09:59,791 --> 00:10:01,583
[TWOEARLE laughs]

220
00:10:01,666 --> 00:10:03,375
[AIKA]
I'd better take off.

221
00:10:03,458 --> 00:10:05,333
Whenever you're ready, Twoearle.

222
00:10:05,416 --> 00:10:06,583
[TWOEARLE]
All right, then.

223
00:10:06,666 --> 00:10:09,583
Secret dimensional
transport gate, activate!

224
00:10:11,416 --> 00:10:14,083
Tail On! Ha!

225
00:10:35,458 --> 00:10:36,541
Oh, right.

226
00:10:36,625 --> 00:10:38,208
Thanks for saving me,
Madame President.

227
00:10:38,291 --> 00:10:39,541
[ERINA]
Uh?

228
00:10:39,625 --> 00:10:40,958
[TAILBLUE] Since I've
been fighting as Tailblue,

229
00:10:41,041 --> 00:10:43,833
I've become the laughingstock
of the entire planet.

230
00:10:43,916 --> 00:10:46,666
Some even think that I'm
as bad as Ultimaguil.

231
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,083
But not you. I just
wanted to say thanks

232
00:10:49,166 --> 00:10:51,666
for believing that
Tailblue is a real hero.

233
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,500
[ERINA]
You're welcome.

234
00:10:58,291 --> 00:10:59,208
[TWOEARLE]
All right team,

235
00:10:59,291 --> 00:11:01,791
operation training
session: begin!

236
00:11:01,875 --> 00:11:04,583
[TAILRED] You're able to
transform easily enough.

237
00:11:04,666 --> 00:11:06,125
Now all you have
to do is believe

238
00:11:06,208 --> 00:11:07,625
in your twin-tail attribute.

239
00:11:07,708 --> 00:11:10,666
Look deep inside yourself,
I know you'll find it.

240
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:13,541
I wish that were true.
But I'm not like you, Soji.

241
00:11:13,625 --> 00:11:15,750
I don't have that
kind of power in me.

