00:21:09,333 --> 00:21:11,208
Good job.

487
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:16,416
[TWOEARLE] They're still
not awake yet, huh?

488
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:18,625
They're exhausted.
Let them get some sleep.

489
00:21:18,708 --> 00:21:19,958
After all, they've earned it.

490
00:21:20,041 --> 00:21:21,125
--[STRANGER] Not bad, ladies.
--[TAILRED] Huh?!

491
00:21:21,208 --> 00:21:22,583
[STRANGER]
From the looks of it, the glow

492
00:21:22,666 --> 00:21:25,833
of your twin-tail attribute
burns brighter than ever.

493
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:28,791
[TAILRED]
Who is that?

494
00:21:28,875 --> 00:21:30,875
I'm sensing a tremendous
power from her.

495
00:21:30,958 --> 00:21:32,958
Or maybe it's
attribute strength?

496
00:21:33,041 --> 00:21:34,958
[STRANGER]
You don't know who I am?

497
00:21:35,041 --> 00:21:36,125
Well then.

498
00:21:36,208 --> 00:21:37,166
[TAILRED]
Uh...

499
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:41,916
I am Dark Grasper,
the chief's right hand.

500
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,791
Wait a sec...

501
00:21:42,875 --> 00:21:44,041
Is that Tail Gear?

502
00:21:44,125 --> 00:21:45,166
[DARK GRASPER]
Oh no.

503
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:47,875
This is the robust
armor of Glass Gear.

504
00:21:47,958 --> 00:21:50,666
There is no force in the entire
universe that can compete with

505
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:54,958
the power of glasses attribute,
the power of love for glasses.

506
00:21:55,041 --> 00:21:57,583
I created it so I could
be exactly like you.

507
00:21:57,666 --> 00:21:58,583
Hey, Twoearle.

508
00:21:58,666 --> 00:22:01,500
Wait, Twoearle?
What do you mean?

509
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:03,166
[DARK GRASPER]
Now I am a mighty warrior.

510
00:22:03,250 --> 00:22:06,541
And I report directly to
the chief of Ultimaguil.

511
00:22:06,625 --> 00:22:10,083
I've come to this planet for one
reason and one reason alone.

512
00:22:10,166 --> 00:22:13,875
I want you to fight
alongside me, Twoearle.

513
00:23:49,250 --> 00:23:50,000
[SOJI]
Erina!

514
00:23:50,083 --> 00:23:51,458
Looks like you're our third!

515
00:23:51,541 --> 00:23:52,833
Welcome to the team!

516
00:23:52,916 --> 00:23:54,666
[ERINA] Thanks! But I
still have a long way to go

517
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:56,125
as a member of the Twin Tails,

518
00:23:56,208 --> 00:23:58,333
so I'll work hard and make
sure I get better everyday!

519
00:23:58,416 --> 00:24:00,291
[AIKA] Um, if it's okay,
could I borrow your Tail Gear

520
00:24:00,375 --> 00:24:02,166
once in a while, you know
just for the heck of it?

521
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,291
When we're not
fighting, of course?

522
00:24:03,375 --> 00:24:04,583
[SOJI]
Are you still on that?

523
00:24:04,666 --> 00:24:06,333
[AIKA] They've got to
grow eventually, right?

524
00:24:06,416 --> 00:24:08,375
But for now if I could use
the suit every now and then,

525
00:24:08,458 --> 00:24:09,625
maybe it would help
my self-esteem.

526
00:24:09,708 --> 00:24:11,250
[SOJI]
That's not gonna happen.

527
00:24:11,333 --> 00:24:14,708
Next time: "A Passionate
Debut! Dark Grasper!"

528
00:24:14,791 --> 00:24:16,291
[SOJI, AIKA, ERINA]
Tail On!

